data.description: STUNNING Contemporary-Style home. Face of the house softened by arches and curved corners, giving it a WARM and WELCOMING atmosphere. Come inside and you’ll be AMAZED at the GORGEOUS layout. TONS of UPGRADES and features that are “to die for.” Maple wood cabinets with crown moulding. Granite countertops in the kitchen and bathrooms. Full length mirrors for doors on bedroom closets. SPACIOUS master bathroom that features a garden tub, dual sink AND shower. LOVELY fenced-in backyard for your family’s privacy. Words can’t describe its charm, you MUST SEE for yourself. OWNER IS MOTIVATED! SAYS BRING ME AN OFFER!
